.modal-dialog{role: "document"}
  .modal-content
    .modal-header
      %button.close{"aria-label" => "Close", "data-dismiss" => "modal", type: "button"}
        %span{"aria-hidden" => "true"} Ã—
      %h4#more_than_15Label.modal-title Too many Santas!
    .modal-body
      %h3 Heads up!
      %p At this time, Secret Santa only supports lists of up to 15 people.
      %p
        Soon, we'll be introducing paid options which allows people to purchase
        additional slots in their lists supporting more people.
      %p
        However until then we regret (mostly due to spam and abuse prevention
        reasons) that this limit must be enforced, and we trust you understand
        this decision.
      %hr
      %p.tc= image_tag "santa_with_sack_med.png"
    .modal-footer
      %button.close{"aria-label" => "Thanks, I understand!", "data-dismiss" => "modal", type: "button"}
